      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LET'S GO PIES (1) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 20.01 beating Cabao Nickel. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can make it back-to-back wins. DAWN SAID SO (5) missed the frame last time, finishing 5th (20.33) last time in a TG1-4W at this track. Form here at this distance is strong including five wins. Has good early speed so she should be prominent despite the squeeze draw. Can do much better this time. LIFE'S A JOKE (2) used the rails draw to advantage to get home last time at this track and distance (20.17), scoring by 1.75 lengths. Can measure up again. FANCY IN DESIGN (8) is a last-start placegetter who is in the mix again.",
